    "like_dislike_summary": {
      "pos_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "The quality of infrastructure is very good and outstanding because the college is old but the things and memories are always new.",
          "name": "Sundaram Maurya",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "I liked the discipline of college because ragging is strictly prohibited and id cards are checked strictly",
          "name": "Sundaram Maurya",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "I liked the staff, faculty, infrastructure and overall experience is great because it is a good place to get your degree from, it's professional and highly recommended college to do your BCOM from. Placement also good.",
          "name": "Harsh",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Another aspect I liked was the crowd and the education system.",
          "name": "Harsh",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Social and cultural events and vide during such events",
          "name": "Anonymous",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "The most liked part of my college BMCC is teaching staff. All teachers are very supportive, motivative,",
          "name": "Abhijeet Kawade",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Talking about infrastructure it is very well developed and maintained there is hostel,gym, wifi , library facilities in college",
          "name": "Abhijeet Kawade",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "The events are great. Try volunteering in the same and make contacts.",
          "name": "Vidiksha Pawar",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Many volunteering opportunities to overall improve a persons character and behaviour",
          "name": "Sagar Samanta",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Sports and bcc are on top there are trails going on every month for all sports majorly football, cricket, basketball",
          "name": "AMIT KUMAR SHARMA",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        }
      ],
      "neg_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "Events and functions are focused more that studies.",
          "name": "Sundaram Maurya",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Hostel fees is very high compare to college feess",
          "name": "Sundaram Maurya",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Lack of clarity in decision of the departments.",
          "name": "Harsh",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Some technical difficulty in issuing marksheets.",
          "name": "Harsh",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "The behavior of some teachers and staff is not good",
          "name": "Anonymous",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Library timing it's just only from morning 7 to evening 6 so hosetlors any other students can't study for more time.",
          "name": "Abhijeet Kawade",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "The communication can get better among the students and faculty members.",
          "name": "Anonymous",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "No freshers party for new individual entering the campus and only online orientation on smart board sitting in the classroom",
          "name": "Advita malode",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "There is no interaction between the seniors and juniors. College must conduct that.",
